  "english": [
    "<b>As they too were</b> included <b>in that miracle</b> of the Exodus, they are therefore obligated to participate in the celebration.",
    "<b>Rav Yehuda said</b> that <b>Shmuel said: These four cups must contain</b> enough undiluted wine to allow <b>for diluting a significant cup.</b> In talmudic times, people would not drink pure wine. They would dilute it with water, generally adding three times as much water as wine. If <b>one drank them undiluted,</b> he has <b>fulfilled</b> his obligation. If <b>one drank them all at once,</b> i.e., he poured all four cups of wine into one large cup and drank it, he has <b>fulfilled</b> the obligation. If <b>one gave his sons or the members of his household to drink from them,</b> he has nevertheless <b>fulfilled</b> the obligation.",
    "The Gemara now addresses each of these rulings of Shmuel in turn. Shmuel said that if <b>one drank them undiluted</b> he has <b>fulfilled</b> his obligation. <b>Rava said:</b> He has <b>fulfilled</b> the obligation to drink the four cups of <b>wine,</b> but he has <b>not fulfilled</b> the obligation to drink in a way that expresses <b>freedom,</b> which is the preferable way to fulfill the mitzva, as aristocrats do not drink undiluted wine.",
    "If <b>one drank</b> the four cups <b>all at once, Rav said</b> that he has <b>fulfilled</b> the obligation to drink <b>wine</b> as an expression of rejoicing on the Festival, but he has <b>not fulfilled</b> the obligation to drink <b>four cups,</b> which requires four distinct cups, each drunk separately. Shmuel also stated that if <b>one gave his sons or the members of his household to drink from them,</b> he has nevertheless <b>fulfilled</b> his obligation. <b>Rav Naḥman bar Yitzḥak said: And this is</b> the case only <b>if he</b> himself <b>drank the majority of the cup.</b>",
    "The Gemara <b>raises an objection</b> to the above rulings from a <i>baraita</i>: <b>These four cups must contain</b> one <b>quarter</b>-<i>log</i>, <b>whether</b> the wine <b>is undiluted or diluted, whether</b> it is <b>new or aged. Rabbi Yehuda says: It must have the taste and appearance of wine. In any event,</b> this <i>baraita</i> <b>is teaching</b> that each cup must contain at least the amount <b>of</b> one <b>quarter-</b><i>log</i>, <b>and</b> yet <b>you said</b> that each must contain enough for diluting <b>a significant cup.</b>",
    "<b>They say</b> in response that <b>this and that are one</b> and the same <b>measure.</b> The Gemara explains: <b>What</b> is the meaning of the expression: <b>Enough for diluting a significant cup, which</b> Shmuel <b>said?</b> He meant that there must be enough undiluted wine <b>for each and every one</b> of the cups, i.e., one quarter-<i>log</i> of diluted wine. <b>This</b> amounts to one <b>quarter</b>-<i>log</i> of undiluted wine <b>for all of them</b> combined. A significant cup contains one quarter-<i>log</i>. This quarter-<i>log</i> is comprised of one quarter undiluted wine and three quarters water. Therefore, each cup must contain at least one quarter of one quarter-<i>log</i> of undiluted wine, so that one consumes a full quarter-<i>log</i> of liquid from each cup.",
    "The <i>baraita</i> stated that <b>Rabbi Yehuda says</b> the cup from which one drinks <b>must have</b> the <b>taste and appearance</b> of wine. <b>Rava said: What is the reason</b> for the opinion <b>of Rabbi Yehuda? As it is written: “Look not upon wine when it is red”</b> (Proverbs 23:31). This verse proves that the appearance of wine and not only its taste is important.",
    "<b>The Sages taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i>: <b>All are obligated in these four cups, including men, women, and children. Rabbi Yehuda said: What benefit do children receive from wine?</b> They do not enjoy it. <b>Rather, one distributes to them</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>שֶׁאַף הֵן הָיוּ בְּאוֹתוֹ הַנֵּס. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר רַב יְהוּדָה אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        0,
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁמוּאֵל: אַרְבָּעָה כּוֹסוֹת הַלָּלוּ צָרִיךְ שֶׁיְּהֵא בָּהֶן",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כְּדֵי מְזִיגַת כּוֹס יָפֶה. שְׁתָאָן חַי — יָצָא. שְׁתָאָן",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּבַת אַחַת — יָצָא. הִשְׁקָה מֵהֶן לְבָנָיו וְלִבְנֵי בֵיתוֹ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יָצָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>שְׁתָאָן חַי יָצָא, אָמַר רָבָא: יְדֵי יַיִן — יָצָא, יְדֵי חֵירוּת —",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֹא יָצָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>שְׁתָאָן בְּבַת אַחַת, רַב אָמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יְדֵי יַיִן — יָצָא, יְדֵי אַרְבָּעָה כּוֹסוֹת — לֹא יָצָא. הִשְׁקָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מֵהֶן לְבָנָיו וְלִבְנֵי בֵיתוֹ — יָצָא, אָמַר רַב נַחְמָן בַּר",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יִצְחָק: וְהוּא דְּאִשְׁתִּי רוּבָּא דְכָסָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מֵיתִיבִי: אַרְבָּעָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כּוֹסוֹת הַלָּלוּ צָרִיךְ שֶׁיְּהֵא בָּהֶן כְּדֵי רְבִיעִית,",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֶחָד חַי וְאֶחָד מָזוּג, אֶחָד חָדָשׁ וְאֶחָד יָשָׁן. רַבִּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יְהוּדָה אוֹמֵר: צָרִיךְ שֶׁיְּהֵא בּוֹ טַעַם וּמַרְאֵה יַיִן.",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קָתָנֵי מִיהַת כְּדֵי רְבִיעִית, וְאַתְּ אָמְרַתְּ כּוֹס יָפֶה!",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמְרִי: אִידֵּי וְאִידֵּי חַד שִׁיעוּרָא הוּא, מַאי ״כְּדֵי",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מְזִיגַת כּוֹס יָפֶה״ דְּקָאָמַר — לְכׇל חַד וְחַד, דְּהָוֵי לְהוּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כּוּלְּהוּ רְבִיעִית. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>רַבִּי יְהוּדָה אוֹמֵר: צָרִיךְ שֶׁיְּהֵא",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בּוֹ טַעַם וּמַרְאֶה. אָמַר רָבָא: מַאי טַעְמָא דְּרַבִּי",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יְהוּדָה, דִּכְתִיב: ״אַל תֵּרֶא יַיִן כִּי יִתְאַדָּם״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּנוּ רַבָּנַן:",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַכֹּל חַיָּיבִין בְּאַרְבָּעָה כּוֹסוֹת הַלָּלוּ, אֶחָד אֲנָשִׁים,",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וְאֶחָד נָשִׁים, וְאֶחָד תִּינוֹקוֹת. אָמַר רַבִּי יְהוּדָה: וְכִי מָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תּוֹעֶלֶת יֵשׁ לְתִינוֹקוֹת בְּיַיִן? אֶלָּא מְחַלְּקִין לָהֶן",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>שֶׁאַף הֵן הָיוּ בְּאוֹתוֹ הַנֵּס.</b> כדאמרינן (<a href=\"/sotah/11b\">סוטה דף יא:</a>) בשכר נשים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "צדקניות שבאותו הדור נגאלו וכן גבי מקרא מגילה נמי אמרינן הכי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דמשום דע\"י אסתר נגאלו וכן גבי נר חנוכה במסכת שבת (<a href=\"/shabbat/23a\">ד&#x27; כג.</a>):",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>כְּדֵי מְזִיגַת כּוֹס יָפֶה.</b> שיעורו רובע] רביעית כדי שימזגנו ויעמוד על",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "רביעית לוג דחמרא דלא דרי על חד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תלת מיא לאו חמרא הוא וקא סלקא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דעתך דבין כולם קאמר שמואל דליהוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "רובע רביעית יין: <b>שתאן</b> <b>חי.</b> שלא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מזגו במים: <b>בבת</b> <b>אחת.</b> עירה ארבעתן",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לתוך כוס אחד: <b>ידי</b> <b>יין</b> <b>יצא.</b> ששתה ד'",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כוסות: <b>ידי</b> <b>חירות</b> <b>לא</b> <b>יצא.</b> כלומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אין זו מצוה שלימה: <b>כדי</b> <b>רביעית.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בין כולן קשיא לשמואל דאמר רובע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "רביעית דהיינו כוס יפה: ה\"ג מאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כוס יפה דקאמר שמואל לכל חד וחד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דהוו להו כולהו רביעית: <b>אל</b> <b>תרא</b> <b>יין</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<b>כי</b> <b>יתאדם.</b> אלמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Pesachim 108b:2:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
